\f0\b\fs30 \cf0 Raspberry Liqueur\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa320\ql\qnatural

\b0 \cf0 \uc0\u8232 Makes 2 1/2 cups\u8232 1 pint fresh raspberries\u8232 2 1/2 cups Vodka\u8232 1 vanilla bean\u8232 1/4 tsp. whole allspice\u8232 1/2 cup simple syrup
\f1\fs42 \

\f0\fs30 \uc0\u8232 Wash berries and lightly crush to release flavor. Add vodka, vanilla bean, and allspice. Stir and store in a large mouthed bottle in cool dark place for 3 weeks. Strain mixture through a cheesecloth and squeeze as much juice as possible. Pour back in bottle, add sugar syrup to taste. Age another 3-5 weeks.
