\f0\b\fs30 \cf0 Limoncello\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa320\ql\qnatural

\b0 \cf0 \uc0\u8232 Makes 1 bottle\u8232 1 bottle (750ml) vodka\u8232 1 cup simple syrup \u8232 7 lemon zests
\f1\fs42 \

\f0\fs30 \uc0\u8232 Wash lemons with a brush and hot water to remove any pesticides or wax and zest the lemons. Pour 1/2 of the vodka in a gallon glass jar and add zest. Cover and let sit at room temperature for 20 days. Add the simple syrup and remaining vodka and let sit for another 20 days.
